OL,3,CHuge 50ft sinkhole appears at end of
OL,4,Cresident's drive as homes evacuated
OL,6,FResidents have been told to avoid the
OL,7,Farea after a large sinkhole appeared
OL,8,Fon a housing estate in Merthyr Tydfil.
OL,10,FThe sinkhole opened up on Sunday, 1
OL,11,FDecember, at Nant Morlais, Pant,
OL,12,Fleading to 30 homes being evacuated.
OL,14,FThe sinkhole was caused by a collapsed
OL,15,Fculvert ` a structure which allows
OL,16,Fwater to flow under roads and railways.
OL,18,FThe sinkhole has continued to expand,
OL,19,Fwith further cracks appearing in the
OL,20,Froad surface, Merthyr Tydfil Council's
OL,21,Fleader has said.
