OL,6,F"I came home and the whole of the bit
OL,7,Fthere was barricaded off, and the hole
OL,8,Fjust gradually got worse and worse as
OL,9,Fit was opening up. I couldn't see down
OL,10,Fto the bottom, but it was a good
OL,11,Fdepth, it was really quite deep."
OL,13,FMerthyr Tydfil Council leader Brent
OL,14,FCarter said: "It seems to be getting
OL,15,Fbigger, there's more cracks coming
OL,16,Facross the road and into walls and
OL,17,Fgardens."
