OL,6,FHe added that two landslides which
OL,7,Frecently occurred further up the
OL,8,Fmountain had caused stone to come down
OL,9,Fand come crashing straight through the
OL,10,Fculvert. While Councillor Carter said
OL,11,Fhe hoped residents would be back in
OL,12,Ftheir homes by Christmas, he said he
OL,13,Fcould not give a timeline for how long
OL,14,Fit would take for remediation works to
OL,15,Fbe completed.
