OL,6,FHe added that they hope to block off
OL,7,Fthe water and then the culvert could
OL,8,Fbe inspected and remediation work can
OL,9,Fbe completed. He thanked the residents
OL,10,Fwho have been evacuated for their
OL,11,Funderstanding.
OL,13,FHe continued: "(On Sunday) we were
OL,14,Ftrying to get people out of their
OL,15,Fhomes and into temporary accommodation
OL,16,F` to pack a bag all within 15 minutes'
OL,17,Fnotice, it's traumatic, I've got every
OL,18,Fsympathy for them, it's a terrible
OL,19,Ftime.
