OL,6,F"Our team and the officers of the
OL,7,Fcouncil, as well as external agencies,
OL,8,Fare moving heaven and earth to ensure
OL,9,Feverything is put back into place as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible, but obviously safety
OL,11,Fis paramount."
OL,13,FConcerns about the culvert have been
OL,14,Fraised in the past and he said it is
OL,15,Finspected every two years to try to
OL,16,Fensure something like this does not
OL,17,Fhappen. He added that more frequent
OL,18,Finspections may be considered going
OL,19,Fforward.
