OL,3,CHuge 50ft sinkhole appears at end of
OL,4,Cresident's drive as homes evacuated
OL,6,FIn a statement, Merthyr Tydfil Council
OL,7,Fpreviously warned residents to stay
OL,8,Faway from the area.
OL,10,F"Council officers and police have been
OL,11,Fonsite at Nant Morlais, Pant, working
OL,12,Fwith other agencies at the site of a
OL,13,Fsinkhole," the statement said. "No
OL,14,Ffurther help or support is needed at
OL,15,Fthis time but thank you to everyone
OL,16,Fwho has offered it. Safety is our main
OL,17,Fpriority. To allow engineers to keep
OL,18,Fworking safely, please stay away from
OL,19,Fthe area."
